  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 58209c6e5a952e54b90c6c0dde0b23dc, type: 3}
  m_Name: Quest6_Talk_Chief
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Quest
  QuestID: Quest6
  QuestName: Meet the Village Chief
  LevelRequirment: 0
  Instructions: You know, for someone who washed up on this beach not long ago, you've
    made quite an impression. There's someone you should meet. He's the Chief of
    this town, stays in the large hut at the north end. He doesn't see just anyone,
    but I have a feeling he'll make an exception for you. Tell him Aluna sent you.
  Deliver: Aluna sent you. Interesting. Sit down. I've heard whispers about a stranger
    on the island... I had a feeling you'd find your way to me eventually. You're
    looking for something. I can see it.
